translate English s039_cb91a234:
    voice "KOHARU_0453"
    koharu "「Makoto-chan, is the hairdryer too hot?」"


translate English s039_15eb60f1:
    voice "MAKOTO_0388"
    makoto "「Mnh... it's all right...」"


translate English s039_fd776205:
    voice "MAKOTO_0389"
    makoto "「Koharu... thank you for drying my hair...」"


translate English s039_64ff8a4a:
    voice "KOHARU_0454"
    koharu "「I always hoped I could dry these long hairs of yours like this at least once, Makoto-chan.」"


translate English s039_454edbd9:
    voice "MAKOTO_0390"
    makoto "「So you did...」"


translate English s039_c296bbd5:
    voice "KOHARU_0455"
    koharu "「Your hair is so very beautiful, Makoto-chan.」"


translate English s039_72ad2a7a:
    voice "MAKOTO_0391"
    makoto "「I-, it is?」"


translate English s039_0ec591e3:
    voice "KOHARU_0456"
    koharu "「Yes!」"


translate English s039_5cad97f7:
    voice "MAKOTO_0392"
    makoto "「Maybe it's just because you're drying it so thoroughly, Koharu...」"


translate English s039_b0d4b966:
    voice "KOHARU_0457"
    koharu "「Oh no, I think your hair is beautiful even when you are at school.」"


translate English s039_387ec132:
    voice "MAKOTO_0393"
    makoto "「Even at school...」"


translate English s039_ace8ca47:
    voice "KOHARU_0458"
    koharu "「Yes. And also, they smell so nice.」"


translate English s039_1d7ee9b4:
    voice "KOHARU_0459"
    koharu "「Even at school I often spot people turning around and looking at you, Makoto-chan.」"


translate English s039_8b99d81c:
    voice "MAKOTO_0394"
    makoto "「I thought that was simply because I'm tall of stature, and so they think I'm weird...」"


translate English s039_df6d0a00:
    voice "KOHARU_0460"
    koharu "「That is not true! They were aaall gazing and would not look away.」"


translate English s039_b6425f5b:
    voice "MAKOTO_0395"
    makoto "「They were...?」"


translate English s039_e623ccb5:
    voice "KOHARU_0461"
    koharu "「Yes!」"


translate English s039_083a9f6a:
    voice "KOHARU_0462"
    koharu "「And then, I only learned it now, but, with your hair down you look so very adult.」"


translate English s039_d5de64d7:
    voice "MAKOTO_0396"
    makoto "「So I look aged...」"


translate English s039_61b017ef:
    voice "KOHARU_0463"
    koharu "「Adult, I said! Somewhat like a princess.」"


translate English s039_e5f655bd:
    voice "MAKOTO_0397"
    makoto "「Princess...!」"


translate English s039_48027f76:
    voice "MAKOTO_0398"
    makoto "「...that would never be.」"


translate English s039_ff262860:
    voice "KOHARU_0464"
    koharu "「That is not true!」"


translate English s039_9802062f:
    voice "KOHARU_0465"
    koharu "「I am so glad we could have a sleepover today, because I could see you looking like this, Makoto-chan.」"


translate English s039_5626cb47:
    voice "MAKOTO_0399"
    makoto "「Come now...」"


translate English s039_16c5ce66:
    voice "KOHARU_0466"
    koharu "「I am serious here!」"


translate English s039_d6aa4d77:
    voice "KOHARU_0467"
    koharu "「Because I am together with the pretty, stylish, calm, and cool Makoto-chan!」"


translate English s039_ccc2c6b2:
    voice "MAKOTO_0400"
    makoto "「Awww...」"


translate English s039_b5b1b98e:
    voice "KOHARU_0468"
    koharu "「Your hair will be dry soon, I think.」"


translate English s039_dd2cb6fd:
    voice "MAKOTO_0401"
    makoto "「T-, thank you...」"


translate English s039_c0ef01e8:
    voice "KOHARU_0469"
    koharu "「Happy to be of help.」"


translate English s039_5c7ec763:
    voice "MAKOTO_0402"
    makoto "「Awwww... my face feels all hot...」"


translate English s039_33867845:
    voice "KOHARU_0470"
    koharu "「I knew it, the hairdryer was too hot?!」"


translate English s039_50a770bb:
    voice "MAKOTO_0403"
    makoto "「No, that's not the hairdryer, it's...」"


translate English s039_816be7b5:
    voice "MAKOTO_0404"
    makoto "「Being praised that much... it's awkward...」"


translate English s039_1090b020:
    voice "KOHARU_0471"
    koharu "「Praise, really... I only said what was on my mind.」"


translate English s039_48628f00:
    voice "MAKOTO_0405"
    makoto "「Awww...」"


translate English s039_20a6061e:
    voice "KOHARU_0472"
    koharu "「*Sniiiff*... heh, Makoto-chan, your hair smells so nice~.」"


translate English s039_9956f01c:
    voice "MAKOTO_0406"
    makoto "「Today we have the same smell...」"


translate English s039_9148eab8:
    voice "KOHARU_0473"
    koharu "「Yes!」"


translate English s039_c36a4a67:
    voice "MAKOTO_0407"
    makoto "「Koharu, is your hair dry already...?」"


translate English s039_2b1636c8:
    voice "KOHARU_0474"
    koharu "「No, I am yet to start.」"


translate English s039_a8021857:
    voice "MAKOTO_0408"
    makoto "「C-, could I dry it, maybe?」"


translate English s039_c56d961b:
    voice "KOHARU_0475"
    koharu "「Eh!」"


translate English s039_84bad330:
    voice "MAKOTO_0409"
    makoto "「If you don't want to it's okay...」"


translate English s039_cd2e5d22:
    voice "KOHARU_0476"
    koharu "「No, no, if you would like to, then please do.」"


translate English s039_d5914322:
    voice "MAKOTO_0410"
    makoto "「...yes!」"


translate English s039_3afa5af6:
    voice "KOHARU_0477"
    koharu "「Eheheh...」"


translate English s039_e36af45d:
    voice "MAKOTO_0411"
    makoto "「Your hair is short, Koharu, so it'll dry right away...」"


translate English s039_10548304:
    voice "KOHARU_0478"
    koharu "「But it is so thin and all rough.」"


translate English s039_227edd54:
    voice "KOHARU_0479"
    koharu "「I so want to try a fluffier and cuter hairstyle.」"


translate English s039_80545d3d:
    voice "MAKOTO_0412"
    makoto "「You mean even cuter than now...?!」"


translate English s039_0c27df3c:
    voice "KOHARU_0480"
    koharu "「Is that even so shocking?」"


translate English s039_dc52a40d:
    voice "MAKOTO_0413"
    makoto "「Of course.」"


translate English s039_418c9d25:
    voice "KOHARU_0481"
    koharu "「I-, I see...」"


translate English s039_532112e2:
    voice "MAKOTO_0414"
    makoto "「Just imagining it... it is, and plenty...」"


translate English s039_627dbf04:
    voice "KOHARU_0482"
    koharu "「I am not sure I understand why, but when you tell me that, Makoto-chan, my heart goes puff and gets all warm.」"


translate English s039_32511804:
    voice "KOHARU_0483"
    koharu "「Maybe... it is because I am very happy, I think.」"


translate English s039_92cd6c6d:
    voice "MAKOTO_0415"
    makoto "「Koharu...」"


translate English s039_06975e05:
    voice "KOHARU_0484"
    koharu "「Would you... stay together with me forever, even after today?」"


translate English s039_23706ab7:
    voice "MAKOTO_0416"
    makoto "「Yes...」"


translate English s039_22d3b1c4:
